quick instructions
  - get firebreath (http://www.firebreath.org/)
  - copy the folder firebreath_project/OOCaller 
    to your $FIREBREATH_HOME/projects folder
  - follow the firebreath instructions to pre-
    pare and compile the plugin
  - copy the generated native plugin to the 
    extension folder for your operating system
  - follow the browser instructions to install
    the extension
  - check with the testplugin.html page if
    the extension runs well (change the urls 
    to your needs)

for questions or recomendations please send me 
an email at magomi+github@gmail.com or contact 
me directly at github (http://github.com/magomi)

